ObAgent: uncertain

The symptoms are elevated inter-service RPC latencies (p95/mean rises across many services), which could be network latency or service-side slowdowns (e.g., CPU contention). To disambiguate, run:
- whether_is_abnormal_metric on host/pod CPU (e.g., host.cpu.percent or container.cpu.user) for the affected services;
- whether_is_abnormal_metric on network indicators (tcp.retransmits, net.if.tx_errors / rx_errors, interface latency);
- check socket/error logs for connection resets;
- collect_trace on representative requests to see span-level breakdown (time in network vs server processing).
